1.title: School Bus Story
1.plot: Meet Doc McWheelie. She is a Car Doctor. Cars, Buses and other vehicles come to her garage for repairs. Come and see what happens in her Mechanical Workshop.

2.title: Fast Sports Car
2.plot: Meet Doc McWheelie the Car Doctor. Today she repairs a Red Sports Car. Cars, Buses and other vehicles come to her garage for Mechanical Repairs. Come and see what happens in her Workshop.

3.title: Car & Tow Truck
3.plot: Today in Doctor Mac Wheelie's Garage, she repairs a cute Yellow Car with a flat tyre. Cars, Buses and other vehicles come to her garage for Mechanical Repairs. Come and see what happens in her Workshop.

4.title: Christmas Winter Truck
4.plot: Doc McWheelie meets a Truck that must change it's tires for the Winter season. Let's see how she turns a Truck into a special Winter Truck.

5.title: Clean a Cartoon SUV! (Suburban Utility Vehicle)
5.plot: A Suburban Utility Vehicle (SUV) is an amazing vehicle but it can get really dirty driving around. Come and see how Doc McWheelie makes it shiny and clean again with shampoo, brushes, wax and water.

6.title: Doc McWheelie's Yellow Car
6.plot: Doc McWheelie's friend the Yellow Car meets two Trucks and they all decide to go for a picnic. But there are some problems. Come and see what they are.

7.title: Car Engine Repair
7.plot: Tow Truck brings a sick car to Doc McWheelie. Let's Learn all about Car Engines, engine oil and air filters with Doc McWheelie. Buses and Cars come to her Garage with problems to get repaired. Come and see what happens in her Mechanical Workshop.

8.title: Electric Sports Car Rescue
8.plot: Watch what happens when Doc McWheelie tries to repair this black sports car. She gets confused. Cars, Buses and other vehicles come to her garage for repairs. Come and see what happens in her Mechanical Workshop.

9.title: Headlights
9.plot: In the Repair Garage of Doc McWheelie today is an Off Road ATV Car with Broken Headlight Bulbs but the Doctor knows how to mend them.

10.title: Racing Car
10.plot: Doctor McWheelie meets a Racing Car that cannot race. Let's see what she can do to make it race like the wind.

11.title: Car Factory
11.plot: Doc McWheelie is a girl Mechanic who repairs vehicles in her own Garage but today she will visit a Car Factory with working Robots. She learns about chassis, wheels, engines and metal body shells.

12.title: Truck Repairs & Road Safety
12.plot: Doc McWheelie is a girl Mechanic who repairs vehicles in her own Garage. Today she is visiting the Spare Part Shop and she finds a Car to Repair.

13.title: Truck Transformers
13.plot: Garbage Truck and Excavator and Cement Mixer want to do each other's jobs.

14.title: Car Trailer
14.plot: Let's Move House. We will need a Car Trailer so first we need to ask Doc McWheelie how to use one.

15.title: Fixing the Bridge
15.plot: This vehicle transforms from a Cement Mixer to a Crane to Garbage Truck.

16.title: Toy Car
16.plot: Let's Learn about Batteries, Battery-powered Toy Cars and Radio-controlled Vehicles with Doc McWheelie.

17.title: Gas Tank Repair
17.plot: Pretty Purple Problem. A Cartoon Car's fuel tank is damaged and the petrol is leaking away. Can Doc McWheelie repair it?

18.title: Secret Monster Truck
18.plot: Today Doc McWheelie is showing off her Monster Truck. Come and see what it can do.

19.title: Tow Truck Breakdown
19.plot: Car Doctor meets a Tow Truck who is not strong enough to carry a Tractor. The poor Tow Truck breaks down ...but Doc McWheelie can help to fix it. She collects all her tools and goes to help!. Can Doc McWheelie repair it?

20.title: The Robot
20.plot: Dr MacWheelie is unhappy. She is so busy fixing and repairing Cars and Vehicles - She needs an assistant to assist her so she builds her own robot helper on a 3D printer. It's strong and can carry things. Come and meet "Handy" the robot.

21.title: Robot Breaks Car
21.plot: The robot breaks a Sports Car but Doc McWheelie teaches it Mechanics. Have you met "Handy"?

22.title: Truck gets Stuck
22.plot: A big Truck carrying a house gets stuck under a Road Bridge but Doc McWheelie the Car Doctor knows what to do.

23.title: Packing for London
23.plot: Doc McWheelie is going on Holiday to London so she must Pack her suitcase and get a taxi to the Airport. Come and help us pack for her Holiday.

24.title: Ride a London Bus
24.plot: Doctor MacWheelie goes on Holiday to England. She is in London and she rides a London double-decker Bus. Come sight-seeing with us to Big Ben and London Bridge and take a London Taxi Cab. Learn about the different Traffic Rules in England.

25.title: Parktronic
25.plot: Robot Handy is driving to the Airport to meet Doc McWheelie but he has a Car Crash while trying to park the Car. Let's Learn about Parking and ParkTronic parking sensors.

26.title: Call an Ambulance
26.plot: Call a Doctor for Car Doctor. Doc McWheelie gets sick. What's wrong? Let's Learn about Health and Medicine with these 2 Doctors.

27.title: Magic Limousine
27.plot: Watch how Doctor MacWheelie makes an old car change into a limousine in her Garage. It becomes like a house with a sofa and a kitchen. Incredible.

28.title: Save a Desert Jeep
28.plot: Doctor MacWheelie travels to the desert on her ATV to help an Jeep that has a problem. It's very hot in the Desert but she uses GPS to find the Jeep. The Jeep's engine has overheated but Doctor MacWheelie can fix everything.

29.title: Caravan gets Lost
29.plot: Poor Little Caravan gets lost on Holiday. Luckily, Doctor McWheelie is here to rescue it and we discover about Space Satellite Navigation and how GPS works. It's simple.

30.title: Tank Tractor
30.plot: Doctor MacWheelie turns a battle tank from into a farm tractor with help from Handy the Robot.

imdb.title: Doctor MacWheelie
plot: Doctor Mac Wheelie - new kid's cartoon about cars, wheels, trucks and toy cars. Doctor Mac Wheelie is a kid's story about a cheerful little girl car doctor.
